{"tid":1412610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香城online線上集會副本(大埔區)路線","createTime":"2019-08-05T07:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T07:41:54.000Z","uid":260041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ad419d5cde9ef340e8abf816741f7e91b082c7c6","tid":1412610,"uid":260041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香城online釋出多個線上多人集會地圖，朝聖果陣可能有好多怪，唔知幾時會由中立變主動攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以做定功課角色就無禁易死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n風水廣場齋睇地圖算係四方八達既地方。<br />\n<br />\n  沿汀角路上去工廠區，往下係舊墟遊樂場。<br />\n  遊樂場往消防局行可以去太和站，往公立學校方向可以去寶鄉(一田方向有狗屋唔好去)，寶鄉向下行陣就係大埔墟站。所以都幾多路線可以走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過唯一缺點係出生點出黎條路無咩障礙物/小路，一條大直路好易比怪打，有無其他大埔友入黎教路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd51b3eaa8245bcbe53de6f1a96e1675cee9553","tid":1412610,"uid":260041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:19:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"148a87e7a7b15e3052d3d32c9b3fa116e085af06","tid":1412610,"uid":260041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:19:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c84099c58a9ac58b27241ac966b364f967e1fc08","tid":1412610,"uid":260041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:19:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e498b1b5620d5a1320dd9f267e3dbc9edf3c8d7","tid":1412610,"uid":282560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad419d5cde9ef340e8abf816741f7e91b082c7c6","tid":1412610,"uid":260041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香城online釋出多個線上多人集會地圖，朝聖果陣可能有好多怪，唔知幾時會由中立變主動攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以做定功課角色就無禁易死啦<img src=\"/a